require(corrplot)
df <- read.csv("MetalsRaw.csv")
df <- df[,-1]
corr_metals <- cor(df)
corrplot.mixed(corr_metals, lower = 'shade', upper = 'pie', 
               tl.pos = "lt", tl.col = "black", tl.cex = 1.8)
